x\geq 0
 \frac{\mathrm d}{\mathrm dx} \left[ \log\Big(x+\sqrt{x^2+1}\Big) \right] = \frac{1}{\sqrt{1+x^2}} 
 \int \frac{1}{\sqrt{1+x^2}} \ \!\mathrm dx
